## Problem
`pkg/api/handlers/mcp_resources.go:24-260` has ~12 handlers that repeat the identical pattern:
```go
if isDemoMode(c) {
    return c.JSON(demoData)
}
client := getK8sClient(c)
if client == nil {
    return handleK8sError(c, ...)
}
// actual logic
```

This is ~10 lines repeated 12 times = ~120 lines of pure boilerplate.

## Proposed Fix
Extract a `withDemoFallback[T](demoData T, handler func(c *fiber.Ctx, client K8sClient) error) fiber.Handler` helper that:
1. Checks demo mode → returns demo data
2. Gets K8s client → returns error if nil
3. Calls the inner handler with the validated
